{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ScreenOrientation","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen_Orientation_API\">Screen Orientation API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation\"><code>ScreenOrientation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/angle\"><code>angle</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/lock\"><code>lock()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/unlock\"><code>unlock()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Screen Orientation API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation\"><code>Screen.orientation</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>ScreenOrientation</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen_Orientation_API\">Screen Orientation API</a> provides information about the current orientation of the document.</p>\n<p>A <strong><code>ScreenOrientation</code></strong> instance object can be retrieved using the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation\"><code>screen.orientation</code></a> property.</p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"88\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"44\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      EventTarget\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"88\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"118\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"88,14 98,9 98,19 88,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"118\" y=\"0\" width=\"136\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"186\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      ScreenOrientation\n    </text>\n  </a></svg>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"screenorientation.type\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/type\"><code>ScreenOrientation.type</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns the document's current orientation type, one of \"portrait-primary\", \"portrait-secondary\", \"landscape-primary\", or \"landscape-secondary\".</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"screenorientation.angle\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/angle\"><code>ScreenOrientation.angle</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns the document's current orientation angle.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"event_handlers","title":"Event handlers","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"screenorientation.onchange\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>ScreenOrientation.onchange</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events/Event_handlers\">event handler</a> called whenever the screen changes orientation.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"screenorientation.lock\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/lock\"><code>ScreenOrientation.lock()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Locks the orientation of the containing document to its default orientation and returns a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"screenorientation.unlock\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/unlock\"><code>ScreenOrientation.unlock()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Unlocks the orientation of the containing document from its default orientation.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/screen-orientation/#screenorientation-interface","title":"The Screen Orientation API"}],"query":"api.ScreenOrientation"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.ScreenOrientation","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The ScreenOrientation interface of the Screen Orientation API provides information about the current orientation of the document.","popularity":0.0017,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:18:40.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/screenorientation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/screenorientation/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/e0e09b1df51489867f2e74c18586d168ba5e00d1","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation","title":"ScreenOrientation"}],"pageTitle":"ScreenOrientation - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}